        be used to convert numbers to strings:


#) Converting Dates to Numbers:
    - The global method Number() can be used to convert dates to numbers.
        d = new Date(); 
        document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = Number(d);  // 1773231679164
    
    - The date method getTime() does the same.
        d = new Date(); 
        document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = d.getTime();  // 1773231679164


#) Converting Dates to Strings:
    - The global method String() can convert dates to strings.
        String(Date());     // Wed Mar 11 2026 18:08:56 GMT+0545 (Nepal Time)
    
    - The Date method toString() does the same.
        Date().toString();     // Wed Mar 11 2026 18:08:56 GMT+0545 (Nepal Time)
    
